<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.8.5">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2019-06-27T13:20:42+00:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Blog - Robert Horvath</title><subtitle>Blog für dies und das</subtitle><entry><title type="html">Azure DevOps - Xamarin.iOS buildtool versions</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/AzureDevOpsXamarin/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Azure DevOps - Xamarin.iOS buildtool versions" /><published>2019-06-27T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-06-27T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/AzureDevOpsXamarin</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/AzureDevOpsXamarin/">&lt;p&gt;Xamarin.iOS task handles buildtool version a bit different, than other Azure DevOps Task.&lt;br /&gt;
Basically, there’s a shells script on each macOS hosted VM, with which one can select the build tool vesion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This example sets the Xamarin SDK Version (mono version resp.) to a given version:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-yaml highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;steps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pi&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;pi&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pi&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;sudo $AGENT_HOMEDIRECTORY/scripts/select-xamarin-sdk.sh 5_18_1&lt;/span&gt; 
  &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;displayName&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pi&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;Select&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;Xamarin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;SDK&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;version'&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

